                        and <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_26591"
                           >991</ref>. For a glossary of terms found in this work entitled
                           <title>Rang-i Bahār</title> by ‘Abd al-Bāqī, see <ref
                           target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/work_7106"><idno>Persian MS
                              477</idno></ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
